    instruction: [
      `Sit with your feet about six inches apart pointing straight, knees in line between ankles and hips. Use the  muscles of your hip to tilt your pelvis forward to create a little bit of an arch in your lower back`,
      `1. Now keep your arms relaxed and you are going to make big circles with your shoulders start by going up and back down.`,
    ],
